      "comment": "EUREKA JO (2) has switched to the Jason Grimson stable since a decent effort here three weeks ago when she drew on the back row and raced wide before finishing fifth. Has a good record at this shorter distance and is much better served by the low draw. GOLDEN SHOOZ (6) produced a good effort at her latest appearance, coming from the back row and finishing second at this circuit and distance. Building in fitness so could be close to a win. SWEET DIOR NZ (9) is in the mix following respectable thirds from this row at her last two appearances here. CHANGE TACT NZ (8) raced parked but was too good in scoring last start by 2 metres at Menangle. Draws for a trail and could measure up.",
